text: Luis Felipe Corredor Ramos (born 23 September 1997) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Zulia F.C. in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at Football Database Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Aragua FC players Category:Zulia F.C. players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Venezuelan footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Sportspeople from Maracay
